title: BONUS: BobbyCast #161 - Artists Who Hate Playing Their Hits with Bobby and Eddie
itunes:title: BONUS: BobbyCast #161 - Artists Who Hate Playing Their Hits with Bobby and Eddie
description:
Bobby and Eddie talk about 9 artists who hated their biggest hits. From Oasis "Wonderwall" to Miley Cyrus "Party in the USA". Bobby and Eddie talk about the stories behind why the hated the songs and sometimes refused to play them live.
